Notes
-----
- xresources applies cleanly but conflicts at link time with dst's config.c
  (use xresources-reload instead which doesn't conflict)
- Colorscheme patches are runtime-configurable via ~/.config/dst/config colorN
- Patch files prefixed "st-" map to st.suckless.org category by stripping
  the "st-" prefix and replacing hyphens with underscores
